  "voice_observations": {
    "caption_text": "𝐏𝐢𝐧𝐤 𝐏𝐢𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬 𝐑𝐨𝐚𝐝𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐰 𝐢𝐬 𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐞! 🎀\n\nThis October, we’re taking our reformer Pilates 𝐨𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐫𝐨𝐚𝐝 in support of 𝐛𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐬𝐭 𝐜𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐫 𝐚𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬, teaming up with @taviactive 💪✨.\n\nJoin us at these clubs for 45 minutes of full-on Pilates energy — whether you’re a beginner or intermediate, we’ve got a class for you:\n\n📍𝐌𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝐭𝐡 – 𝐃𝐮𝐛𝐚𝐢 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐚 𝐂𝐢𝐭𝐲\n5:30pm Intermediate | 6:30pm Beginner | 7:30pm Intermediate\n👩‍🏫 Coach @_pinipom_21\n\n📍 𝐖𝐞𝐝𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟐𝐧𝐝 – 𝐁𝐚𝐲 𝐆𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐮𝐛𝐚𝐢\n4:30pm Advanced | 5:30pm Intermediate | 6:30pm Beginner\n👩‍🏫 Coach @sonitakruz\n\n📍 𝐅𝐫𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟒𝐭𝐡 – 𝐃𝐮𝐛𝐚𝐢 𝐒𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐨𝐧 𝐎𝐚𝐬𝐢𝐬\n3:00pm Beginner | 4:00pm Intermediate | 5:00pm Advanced\n👩‍🏫 Coach @gxulma\n\n𝐁𝐨𝐨𝐤 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐜𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐬 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐨𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐢𝐭𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐅𝐢𝐫𝐬𝐭 𝐌𝐄𝐍𝐀 𝐀𝐩𝐩.📲\n𝐎𝐍𝐋𝐘𝐀𝐓𝐅𝐈𝐓𝐍𝐄𝐒𝐒𝐅𝐈𝐑𝐒𝐓♥️\n\n#FitnessFirstMe #AboveAndBeyond #GoFurtherWithFitnessFirst #PinkPilates #BreastCancerAwareness #PilatesOnTheRoad #FitnessForACause #ReformerPilates",
